'From Squeak2.8alpha of 13 January 2000 [latest update: #2096] on 10 May 2000 at 9:17:20 pm'!"Change Set:		MIMEHeaderValuePatchDate:			10 May 2000Author:			Steve ElkinsThis is a temporary patch for a bug reported by Bijan Parsia."!!MIMEHeaderValue class methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'sge 5/10/2000 21:11'!fromString: aString 	| parts newValue parms temp |	parts _ ReadStream on: (aString findTokens: ';').	newValue _ self new mainValue: parts next asLowercase.	parms _ Dictionary new.	parts do: 		[:e | 		temp _ e withBlanksTrimmed findTokens: '="'.		temp size = 2 			ifTrue: [parms at: temp first put: temp second]].	newValue parameters: parms.	^ newValue! !